As of June 2011, we expect GHC 7 and cabal-install >= 0.10.2.  Use a recent
cabal-dev as well (something like 0.7.4.x on Cabal 1.10.x).

Follow the instructions below with <repo root>/LLVM as your current
directory.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To use the ABC backend (recommended):

1. Check out the abcBridge repo.
2. $ cabal-dev install . ../Verinf <abcBridge location>

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To DISABLE the ABC backend (uses the Aiger package):

1. Check out the Aiger repo.
2. $ cabal-dev install . ../Verinf <Aiger location> --flags=-abc-backend

[]

